---
// src/components/home/Hero.astro
---
<!-- Header / Hero Section -->
<header class="text-white bg-[#411FEB] p-8 lg:px-32 transition-colors duration-200">
    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch gap-4 mb-8">
        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="flex justify-start lg:justify-end lg:w-1/2 order-1 lg:order-2 mb-4">
            <img src="/assets/media/photo.webp" alt="Photo de Florian Gertner Kilian" fetchpriority="high" loading="eager"
                class="h-full lg:max-h-[250px] rounded-xl shadow-lg object-cover" width="250" height="250">
        </div>
        <!-- Texte -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center order-2 lg:order-1 gap-6">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Florian <span class="uppercase">Gertner Kilian</span></h1>
                <h2 class="text-stroke lg:text-5xl text-4xl font-bold mt-2">
                    <span id="typewriter"></span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <p>Je crée des interfaces premium et intuitives en alliant clarté, esthétique et storytelling pour
                offrir la meilleure expérience possible aux utilisateurs.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                <a href="/services/"
                    class="bg-white text-[#411FEB] px-6 py-3 font-semibold rounded-xl w-full lg:w-auto text-center transition-colors hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-[#3215c7]">
                    Alors, on collabore ?
                </a>
                <a href="/creations/"
                    class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 font-semibold rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full md:w-auto transition-all hover:bg-white/20">
                    Découvrir mes créations
                    <i class='bx bx-arrow-up-right'></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Brands -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden relative brands-carousel-wrapper">
        <div class="brands-scroll flex items-center gap-16 lg:gap-24">
            <!-- Logos will be automatically duplicated by brands_carousel.js -->
            <a href="https://www.phoq.tv" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-80 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/assets/media/brands/PHOQTV.svg" alt="PHOQ.tv" class="h-8 object-contain">
            </a>
            <a href="https://jobbrr.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-80 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/assets/media/brands/JOBBRR.svg" alt="JOBBRR" class="h-8 object-contain">
            </a>
            <a href="https://digitalunicorn.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-80 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/assets/media/brands/Digital Unicorn.svg" alt="Digital Unicorn"
                    class="h-8 object-contain">
            </a>
            <a href="https://game4creator.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-80 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/assets/media/brands/Game4Creator.png" alt="Game4Creator" class="h-8 object-contain">
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.mafigue.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-80 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/assets/media/brands/Mafigue.svg" alt="Mafigue" class="h-8 object-contain">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
